title: Supreme Master Television's 4th Anniversary well wishes 3

json.text: Four years ago, on September 7, Supreme Master Television had our inaugural broadcasts in
Europe and parts of Africa. Through the grace of the Providence, we are now able to air
our programs across the globe and around the clock. We humbly offer our profound gratitude
to Supreme Master Ching Hai for her enlightened vision, compassionate guidance, and loving
care, which has enabled our channel to come into existence and reach so many. Today and
for the entire week, we are delighted to present greetings from dignitaries, celebrities, and
well-wishers on the occasion of Supreme Master Television's 4th Anniversary.
Consulate of the Democratic Republic of Congo in Singapore
Kishore Jethanand Daryanani (M): My name is Kishore Daryanani. I'm the Honorary Consul
for the Democratic Republic of Congo in Africa. Happy 4th Anniversary to Supreme Master Television.
Congratulations with your work. Keep growingï¿½
